description: Gets all batch import jobs or a specific job of the specified ID. This is a paginated API. If you provide a null maxResults, this action retrieves a maximum of 50 records per page. If you provide a maxResults, the value must be between 1 and 50. To get the next page results, provide the pagination token from the GetBatchImportJobsResponse as part of your request. A null pagination token fetches the records from the beginning.

nested_items.name: batchImports
nested_items.description: An array containing the details of each batch import job.

nested_items.name: inputPath
